nf_ingredient_statement: Corn Meal, Cane Sugar, Brown Rice Flour, Whole Grain Oats, Natural Chocolate and Vanilla Flavor, Barley Malt Syrup, Alkalized Cocoa, Expeller-Pressed Canola Oil, Sea Salt, Caramel Color, Natural Vitamin E to Protect Flavor. Vitamins and Minerals: Calcium Carbonate, Iron (Ferrous Sulfate), Vitamin C (Ascorbic Acid), Vitamin B3 (Niacinamide), Vitamin A Palmitate, Vitamin B12, Folic Acid, Vitamin B6 (Pyridoxine Hydrochloride), Vitamin B, (Thiamin Mononitrate), Vitamin B2 (Riboflavin), Vitamin D3.
